rows.name:
The Nopon Radishes that Umama grows...
They're absolutely exquisite, mo.

rows.label: tlk41700122_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Their shape is a little distinctive, and I feel a bit
guilty when I cut them...but it's also a good
way to relieve stress...

rows.label: tlk41700122_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Above all, they taste great... Perfect marks for
both looks and content, mo.

rows.label: tlk41700122_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm so glad I lent that field
to Umama, mo.
